reviewText: An very interesting DVD of K speaking about the reoccurring theme of a crisis in humanity.

Not much to write about...uninspiring.  A waste of time.  Perhaps back in the 60's and 70's this mysteries and aloof approach had its appeal. He is so wrapped up in his own nirvanna and makes it redundently and painfully clear he is not going to share it or reveal anything worth the effort of ones attention.
